properties.areaDesc: Coastal waters from St. Augustine to Flagler Beach FL out 20 NM
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 29 at 8:03PM EST until January 30 at 11:00PM EST by NWS Jacksonville FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...North northeast winds 25 knots with occasional gusts to
gale force possible. Seas 6 to 9 feet with occasional seas up
to 11 feet.

* WHERE...Coastal waters from St. Augustine to Flagler Beach FL
out 20 NM.

* WHEN...From 1 AM to 11 PM EST Thursday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 1 AM TO 11 PM EST THURSDAY
